{"tid":1837173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港政府拒向武漢發出「黑色旅遊警示」","createTime":"2020-01-23T13:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:52:47.000Z","uid":20933,"like":7,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"78065aa97425148d014a3042144bb9c1b6bf3f2a","tid":1837173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:34:45.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎肆虐內地，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良提議，港府應審時度勢向武漢發出最高級別的「黑色旅遊警示」；其他有新型肺炎傳播個案的內地城市，視乎感染人數和傳播速度，發出黃色或紅色旅遊警示級別。<br />\n<br />\n保安局回應，外遊警示制度不包括內地、澳門及台灣，這與其他國家不會就國土內不同地區發出旅遊警示的做法一致。<br />\n<br />\n保安局發言人表示，若有公共衛生理由，保安局會按食物及衛生局建議，就受傳染病嚴重影響的國家或屬地發出外遊警示。因應武漢爆發的新型冠狀病毒，保安局已在「外遊警示制度」網頁及「保安一站通」流動應用程式，發放衛生署相關的旅遊健康建議。"},{"pid":"2858bab48ad70cd8e595a5faa45d3bb33c9bb31e","tid":1837173,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:34:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200123/s00001/1579784490223/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200123%2Fs00001%2F1579784490223%2F&d=3vKtw9Y9osNHyU2tDi1UeI%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=6fae270c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E%2Farticle%2F20200123%2Fs00001%2F1579784490223%2F&h=eccbb64a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/港聞/article/20200123/s00001/1579784490223/</a>"},{"pid":"f4a8af84dcdd57e77b3203f08cd5cc1f9d2d560d","tid":1837173,"uid":57338,"like":34,"dislike":1,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:36:08.000Z","msg":"而家根本就要放大陸人落黎醫"},{"pid":"0264ef6e291fe4088e35f60e0116cfe3cadbf0a7","tid":1837173,"uid":6741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T13:36:28.000Z","msg":"「行動亅「「「開定」」今晚23:59...<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837009\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837009</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n［行動］高鐵送肺炎，所以香港人會自救<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837054\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">htt